  "texts": [
    "The dataset was split into training and validation sets using six-fold cross-validation to compare model performance.",
    "The ratio of training and validation datasets was 5:1.",
    "Of the 4,048 datasets, 3,373 and 675 were used for training and validation, respectively.",
    "In addition, the 2:1 ratio of the high and low QOL groups was configured to remain the same for the training and validation datasets.",
    "To address the data imbalance, owing to the use of 1,336 datasets for the poor QOL group and 2,712 datasets for the high QOL group, we applied oversampling, performed using the synthetic minority oversampling technique (SMOTE)."
  ],
